{"tid":1379453,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有啲說話想同手兄們講","createTime":"2019-07-28T19:26:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T20:30:23.000Z","uid":206691,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ae7757077a71ca3e997dd15fd63b4a4bdc13461b","tid":1379453,"uid":206691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T19:26:14.000Z","msg":"(利申每次都有發夢)<br />\n有幾位朋友都喺極前線   近排夢後檢討時<br />\n發現有一兩位朋友愈發偏激   發夢話要搶犬槍<br />\n打死啲犬  放火燒犬署 打死啲藍絲云云  <br />\n當然我尊重每個手兄嘅決定<br />\n但想提醒下大家<br />\n<br />\n「與怪物戰鬥的人，應當小心自己不要成為怪物。當你凝視深淵，深淵也凝視著你。」<br />\n<br />\n大家要記得為咩而戰呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ed536309e176437fb2975e665e878e332c036d3","tid":1379453,"uid":206691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T19:27:08.000Z","msg":"希望大家記住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84dcdcd37e144211c458a56c2b2ed6e591ebac21","tid":1379453,"uid":206691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T19:28:06.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"fa3736624aca083592e544251b3d1456af405886","tid":1379453,"uid":172465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T20:06:48.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"897591ea23257546fb4eb3f3399043e51a480349","tid":1379453,"uid":207476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T20:09:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">8月5號齊罷工</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">8月5號齊罷工</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">8月5號齊罷工</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">8月5號齊罷工</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">8月5號齊罷工</span></span><br />\n<span styl